messages.subject: Fw: Tell Bush how you'd rate his first 100 days

messages.messageBody:
----- Original Message -----
From: <vote@...>


> Dear Vote.com voter,
>
> This Sunday marks President Bush's 100th day in office. Now you can log
on to http://www.vote.com to tell the president how you'd rate his
performance.
>
> Has Bush provided strong leadership or are people like Dick Cheney and
Colin Powell doing his job for him? Is he looking out for the people's
interests or for special interests?
>
> Tell the president if he's on the right track... or if he needs to change
course. Make your vote count, and ask your friends and family to vote too.
>
> Sincerely,
>
> Your friends at Vote.com
> http://www.vote.com
